?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=pkaA3xZ-kO8Q7kNvgGuXOUj&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=A0or8Rq8cbWaGUWprVQG3sD&oh=00_AYB5w0wd5Vcll9R2dZJ8H7K5RBVHDyR0zzp-_4NY-DahHg&oe=66EE9E6B"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Frame 6.png", "id": "6810280245675752", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982530_6810280249009085_6625958955527266668_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=6X6S7hhQEicQ7kNvgEwQSGn&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=A0or8Rq8cbWaGUWprVQG3sD&oh=00_AYBz7Eq-ruGkna6uH8UcqBgRWeKAR2VEmTrKDamCS0UYtQ&oe=66EEB229"}, "display_name": "GOLF+", "keywords": ["golf", "sports", "multiplayer", "minigolf", "topgolf"], "long_description": "The ultimate VR Golf experience and the official VR Golf game of the PGA TOUR!\n\n**Available on QUEST 2, 3, and Pro**\n\n\u201cThe GOLF+ VR platform is a forward-thinking way to enjoy the sport that is appealing to gamers and golfers of all levels.\u201d - PGA TOUR\n\n\u201cThe visuals are fantastic. It\u2019s like morphing into another universe filled with vibrancy, dynamism and, most important, realism.\u201d - Sports Illustrated\n\n\u201cThe putting function \u2014 which simulator golf has never quite cracked \u2014 is particularly eye-opening.\u201d - GOLF Magazine\n\n\nIncludes:\n\n\u26f3\ufe0f Iconic Courses: 3 Free Courses (Cliffs, Alpine, Castle Links) and 15+ real-world destinations available for purchase including Pebble Beach, The Old Course at St Andrews, TPC Sawgrass and more.\n\n\ud83c\udfcc\ufe0fMultiplayer: Play with your circle of friends, or join public rounds and connect with golf enthusiasts worldwide.\n\n\ud83d\udcc8 Performance Feedback: Advanced shot stats, strokes gained data, handicap system, and swing analyzer to help you understand and improve your game.\n\n\ud83c\udfc6 Competitive Play: Climb the ranks and compete globally on the GOLF+ TOUR, or go head to head in Battle mode.\n\n\u2705 Real Golf Brands: Experience golf equipment from leading brands like Callaway, TaylorMade, and PXG.\n\n\ud83c\udfaf Diverse Modes: From Match Play to Skins, Weekly Challenges and Topgolf, we have an experience for every player.\n\n\ud83c\udfde GOLF+ Clubhouse: A place to practice, fine tune your clubs, and play fun mini-games.\n\n\ud83d\udda5 Media Player: Seamlessly enjoy YouTube and other web media right on the course.", "short_description": "The ultimate VR Golf experience and the official VR Golf game of the PGA TOUR!\n\n**Available on QUEST 2, 3, and Pro**\n\n\u26f3\ufe0f Iconic Courses: 3 Free courses and 15+ real-world destinations available for purchase including Pebble Beach.\n\ud83c\udfcc\ufe0f Multiplayer: Play with friends, or join public rounds.\n\ud83d\udcc8 Performance Feedback: Stats, strokes gained data, and handicap system.\n\ud83c\udfc6 Competitive Play: Compete on the GOLF+ TOUR.\n\ud83c\udfaf Diverse Modes: Match Play to Skins, to weekly challenges and Topgolf Las Vegas.\n"}]}, "developer_name": "Golf Scope Inc.", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.golfplusvr.com/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.golfplusvr.com/terms-and-conditions", "publisher_name": "GolfScope Inc.", "support_website_url": "http://golfplusvr.com/", "website_url": "http://golfplusvr.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2776542286000603"}, {"id": "1573854509480616"}, {"id": "331529188132278"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ADVENTURE", "SIMULATION", "SPORTS"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED_FOR_DOWNLOAD", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["ROOM_SCALE", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking_